      "id": "PopularPost98935",
      "post_content": "This is a totally awesome sliver. It works as the perfect antidote for the [Plague Sliver](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Plague Sliver), not to mention that it can be used with a [Magma Sliver](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Magma Sliver) to create double- or triple-digit life gain, especially with a [Sliver Queen](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sliver Queen) out.  \n  \n@ Kiki Actually, I hear Michigan is really nice this time of year.",
      "posted_by": "beefrocks",
